## âš¡ Quick Start in 60 Seconds

```bash
# 1ï¸âƒ£ Install
curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh

# 2ï¸âƒ£ New project
mkdir demo && cd demo && uv init

# 3ï¸âƒ£ Add dependency
